Data: set of values that convey information

data-layer:
	business-layer: text/images/videos
	application-layer: json/XML
	Data-store(DBs): tables, documents, key-value, trees
	Network-layer: data-packets
	Hardware-layer: bytes  0&1

Data-store:
	Databases
	Queue
	Cache
	Index

Data-flow:
	APIs
	queue
	events

Factors:
	Data-type
	volume/scale
	consumption/retrieval | write/read
	security

key-factor to choose relational vs noSQL
	- schema
	- ACID
	- volume

columnar-data:
	- follow schema but not ACID
	- heavy read/write ex: streaming data

